import React from 'react'; import { mockUsers, mockProjects, mockTasks, mockNotifications } from '../data/mockData'; const Dashboard = () => { const stats = [ { title: 'Total Users', value: mockUsers.length, change: '+12%', changeType: 'positive', icon: 'M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z' }, { title: 'Active Projects', value: mockProjects.filter(p => p.status === 'in-progress').length, change: '+3', changeType: 'positive', icon: 'M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10' }, { title: 'Completed Tasks', value: mockTasks.filter(t => t.status === 'completed').length, change: '+8', changeType: 'positive', icon: 'M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4' }, { title: 'Unread Notifications', value: mockNotifications.filter(n => !n.read).length, change: '-2', changeType: 'negative', icon: 'M15 17h5l-5 5-5-5h5v-5a7.5 7.5 0 1 0-15 0v5h5l-5 5-5-5h5v-5a7.5 7.5 0 1 0 15 0v5z' } ]; const recentTasks = mockTasks.slice(0, 4); const recentNotifications = mockNotifications.slice(0, 3); return (
{/* Header */}

Dashboard

Welcome back! Here's what's happening with your projects.

{/* Stats Grid */}
{stats.map((stat, index) => (

{stat.title}

{stat.value}

{stat.change} from last month

))}
{/* Main Content Grid */}
{/* Recent Tasks */}

Recent Tasks

{recentTasks.map((task) => (

{task.title}

{task.assignee}

{task.priority} {task.dueDate}
))}
{/* Recent Notifications */}

Notifications

{recentNotifications.map((notification) => (

{notification.title}

{notification.message}

{new Date(notification.timestamp).toLocaleDateString()}

))}
{/* Project Progress */}

Project Progress

{mockProjects.map((project) => (

{project.title}

{project.progress}%
{project.team.length} team members {project.status}
))}
); }; export default Dashboard;
